{{Infobox recurring event | name = HeliRussia | native_name = | native_name_lang = | logo = | logo_alt = | logo_caption = | logo_size = | image = RIAN archive 166321 2nd International Business Aviation Exhibition Jet Expo 2007.jpg | image_size = 200px | alt = | caption = A helicopter MD 500 at the 2nd International Business Aviation Exhibition Jet Expo 2007, Crocus-Expo | status = Active | genre = Exhibition | begins = {{start date|2016|5|19}} | ends = {{end date|2016|5|21}} | frequency = Annually | venue = [[Crocus City Mall#Crocus Expo|Crocus Expo]] International Exhibition Center | location = [[Krasnogorsk, Moscow Oblast|Krasnogorsk]], [[Moscow]], [[Russia]] | coordinates = {{coord|55.822686|37.388425|type:event|display=inline,title}} | first = {{start date and age|2008|5|15}} | prev = | next = | participants = 212<ref name=HeliRU-About>{{cite web|title=About|url=http://www.helirussia.ru/en/about/|website=HeliRussia|accessdate=20 October 2015}}</ref> | attendance = 10,000+<ref name=HeliRU-About/> | capacity = | area = Worldwide | activity = | leader_name = | patron = | organised = [[Ministry of Industry and Trade (Russia)|Ministry of Industry and Trade of the Russian Federation]] | filing = | people = | member = | sponsor = | website = {{URL|http://www.helirussia.ru/en/}} | footnotes = }}
[[image:CBOSS_Bell_407.jpg|thumb|right|250px|[[Bell 407]], HeliRussia 2009]]
'''HeliRussia''' is Russia's first International exhibition of [[Helicopter]] Industry held in [[Moscow]], [[Russia]] at [[Crocus City Mall#Crocus Expo|Crocus Expo]] exhibition center. The first show, '''HeliRussia 2008''', was held on May 15–17 2008.
The world achievements in helicopter industry were demonstrated in all aspects, from design to manufacture and operation, on 10 thousand square meter area of the exhibition pavilions and open platforms. Prominent Russian companies like the [[Mil Moscow Helicopter Plant]], [[Kamov]], [[Kazan Helicopter Plant]], Rostvertol, RET Krondshtadt, as well as representative offices of [[Eurocopter]], [[Bell Helicopter Textron]] and other companies participated in HeliRussia 2008.
HeliRussia is an important event in Russian business. The ongoing economic boom in Russia and the growth in paying capacity of the Russian organizations and individuals provide for the steady growth in demand for helicopter-related services.
The exhibition was held by the Russian Helicopter Industry Association with the support of the RF Federal Industrial Agency, the United Industrial Corporation [[Oboronprom]] and OJSC Helicopters of Russia.
