{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2015}} {{Use Australian English|date=January 2015}} {{Infobox music festival | name =Subsonic Music Festival | image = | caption = | location =[[Monkerai]], [[Australia]] | years_active =2008-present | founders = | dates = December | genre = [[Electronic music]], techno, hip hop, etc | attendance = | capacity = | website = {{URL|http://www.subsonicmusic.com.au}} }}
'''Subsonic Music Festival''' is an annual [[electronic music]] festival held since December 2008 in a camping setting in [[Monkerai, New South Wales|Monkerai]], Australia. It was established by Scott Commens (Sydney-based DJ as MSG) and Marco Mazzucco (Sydney-based DJ as Marcotix)<!-- Another co-founder is not named in current sources -->.<ref name="theMusic">{{cite web | url = http://themusic.com.au/festivals/NSW/2014/07/13/subsonic/ | title = Subsonic (NSW) | website = themusic.com.au | accessdate = 11 January 2015 }}</ref><ref name="Giakalis">{{cite web | url = http://www.inthemix.com.au/events/reviews/51818/Subsonic_Music_Festival_2011_Barrington_Tops_NSW_24122011 | title = Subsonic Music Festival 2011 @ Barrington Tops, NSW (2-4/12/2011) | publisher = [[Sound Alliance]] | last = Giakalis | first = Elliot | work = inthemix.com.au | date = 19 December 2011 | accessdate = 11 January 2015 }}</ref>
''TimeOut Sydney''{{'}}s Erin Moy said genres in 2012 included "beats. From thumping four to the floor and tummy-rumbling bass," including dub, techno and hip hop.<ref name="Moy">{{cite news | url = http://www.au.timeout.com/sydney/clubs/events/27351/subsonic-music-festival | title = Subsonic Music Festival – Riverwood Downs Mountain Valley Resort – Clubs | last = Moy | first = Erin | work = TimeOut Sydney | publisher = Time Out Group | accessdate = 11 January 2015 }}</ref> [[Pulse Radio (Australia)|Pulse Radio]] in Australia gave the 2012 event a positive review.<ref>[http://pulseradio.net/articles/2011/12/subsonic-music-festival Subsonic] at [[Pulse Radio (Australia)|Pulse Radio]].</ref> Among the artists that have performed are [[DJ Kentaro]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stoneyroads.com/2012/12/subsonic-music-festival-review|title=Subsonic Music Festival Review|work=Stoney Roads}}</ref> [[James Holden (producer)|James Holden]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.residentadvisor.net/news.aspx?id=26109|title=RA News: James Holden heads to Subsonic 2014|work=Resident Advisor}}</ref> [[Factory Floor]], and Mike Huckaby.
In 2014 it took place at Riverwood Downs Mountain Valley Resort.<ref name="Moy"/><ref>[http://ftp.mixmag.net/words/news/james-holden-addison-groove-named-for-subsonic-festival Subsonic] at ''[[MixMag]]''</ref> ''[[Resident Advisor]]'' editors described that year's festival: "Subsonic has gradually embraced house, techno and other forms of dance music alongside its original staples: psytrance and dub." ''Resident Advisor'' also listed Subsonic on its Top&nbsp;10 November / December 2014 Festivals, from around the world.<ref name="iceresdent">{{cite web|url=http://www.residentadvisor.net/feature.aspx?2315|title=RA: Top 10 November / December 2014 Festivals|work=Resident Advisor}}</ref>
